{"tid":1699360,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你係咪都會行行下無啦啦喊","createTime":"2019-11-08T04:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T20:02:34.000Z","uid":312448,"like":214,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"067bd92c8c73175421c673c371527aa077cd2eff","tid":1699360,"uid":312448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:04:52.000Z","msg":"今朝睇到周同學嘅新聞就好沉重<br />\n依家日常生活做咩都好內疚<br />\n除左好似咩都做唔到 幫唔到手咁之外<br />\n有時仲會諗依家就算行步路 飲啖水咁簡單嘅野 周同學陳同學同埋更加多已經唔喺度嘅手足都做唔到<br />\n佢地一啲又叻游水 一啲又有大學讀 前途一定好過我多多聲<br />\n但係依家死嗰個唔係我<br />\n我寧願我係死嗰個"},{"pid":"c475c9b54f8d42982a133e49be11a9273f8dbf87","tid":1699360,"uid":39723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"手足頂住"},{"pid":"6787061ab907bb09af5188e5480d08b556b0be3b","tid":1699360,"uid":318712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4a591a98bef849ac062cdfa32778a7e724bde0","tid":1699360,"uid":247493,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:08:54.000Z","msg":"呢位手足又唔好咁灰，如果真係好唔開心嘅就抽離一陣唔好睇咁多呢啲新聞先，做下令自己開心嘅野<br />\n我明白而家情況好嚴峻，大家都好唔開心，但係要記住我地唔好花太多時間係過去，而應該諗下係將來我地應該應該做啲咩，等周同學嘅死黎得有意義"},{"pid":"ca33005e854e9c809160aff738d8d7fa2d224cc1","tid":1699360,"uid":145574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:09:19.000Z","msg":"我都喊咗好多日<br />\n喊出嚟都好，唔好屈住<br />\n加油啊手足"},{"pid":"c71c3f78536e5e5ee19d1064a3becb7e59b06dc7","tid":1699360,"uid":277107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:10:28.000Z","msg":"返返下工喊"},{"pid":"802456e9ede3b9bc4decc382adaecd135227935e","tid":1699360,"uid":253169,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682e42448